    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! This car has been so good to me and still drives like a total dream. It\u2019s in great shape, super clean inside, and has clearly been well-loved. I've kept up with all the maintenance, so it's ready for you to just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this beauty go to a great new home!",
