    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver immediate throttle response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. This example has been meticulously maintained with preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle valve actuators to ensure long-term mechanical reliability. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing the M-specific subframe and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to manage cornering loads effectively. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is robust, showing no signs of VANOS rattle or fluid seepage. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well.",
