    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels!",
      "price": 34500.0,
