      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is delivered via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip rear differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced\u2014addressing the critical maintenance items for this platform. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and high-performance dampers, providing the tactile feedback expected of the M-chassis. While showing minor signs of use, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity make this a superb candidate for the spirited driver.",
